    dc:creator "Ďuriš, Zdeněk" ;
    dc:date "2018" ;
    dc:title "Madeirasquilla tuerkayi, a new genus and species of mantis shrimps from Madeira Island, eastern Atlantic (Crustacea: Stomatopoda: Nannosquillidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1206876>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1206878>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1206880> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1206876>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Madeirasquilla tuerkayi gen. et sp. nov., holotype, male. A, anterior part of body, dorsal. B, posterior part of pleon, telson and uropod, dorsal. C, posterior part of pleonite 6and telson, dorsal. D, pleonite 6, telson, and uropod, ventral. E, anterior region of ophthalmic somite, ventral. F, eye, dorsolateral. G, right antenna, dorsal. H, same, lateral. I, right uropod, dorsal.J, left uropodal protopod, ventral.Scale bars, 1 mm; E – unscaled.." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1206876/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1206878>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Madeirasquilla tuerkayi gen. et sp. nov., holotype, male. A, telson, lateral aspect (right side). B, left raptorial appendage, outer side, C–E, left pereiopods 1–3 (resp.), posterior view. F, right male pleopod 1 endopod, anterior view. G, same, apical processes.Scale bars, 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1206878/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.1206880>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Colour patterns of Madeirasquilla tuerkayi gen. et sp. nov. (A, B), and Platysquilla eusebia (Risso, 1816) (C–E) from Madeira Island. A, B, male holotype TL 24.2 mm, habitus and posterior pleon with tail fan (resp.), dorsal. C, ovigerous female, MNHN-IU-2015-1650, TL 42 mm, habitus, dorsal. D, E, pre-ovigerous female, MMF 46567 (TL 43 mm), habitus and posterior pleon with tail fan (resp.), dorsal; orange colour indicates extension of female gonads.Photos, author." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/1206880/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

